NA:3.12\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.12\">3.12 戴勝、戴鵀（hoopoe）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.13\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.13\">3.13 寒鴉（jackdaw）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.14\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.14\">3.14 鳶（kite）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.15\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.15\">3.15 魚鷹（osprey）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.16\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.16\">3.16 鴕鳥（ostrich）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.17\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.17\">3.17 貓頭鷹、鴞（owl）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.18\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.18\">3.18 鷓鴣（partridge）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.19\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.19\">3.19 鵪鶉（quail）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.20\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.20\">3.20 海鷗（seagull）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.21\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.21\">3.21 麻雀、雀鳥（sparrow）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.22\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.22\">3.22 鸛（stork）</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"UBSFaunaLexicon\" data-key=\"FAUNA:3.23\" href=\"#FAUNA:3.23\">3.23 燕子、雨燕（swallow, swift）</a></li>\n</ul></nav>",
